  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">About Me</h1>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
    <p>
      Deep in flow, building stuff, exploring new ideas emerging in software
    </p>
    <p>
      Beautiful people in Prague banking tech inspired me to broaden my perspective.
    </p>
    <p>
      Based in Melbourne. Looking for opportunities in Australia.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of code, I enjoy improv, history, philosophy, volunteering, and nature 
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">What I'm open to</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
      Collaboration on interesting projects, and conversations
      about software, agentic design, and building products.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
